[SN]TITLE[SN]
Man charged over Edinburgh armed robbery

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A 45-year-old man has been charged in connection with an armed robbery at a convenience store in Edinburgh.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The incident happened at the Your Local store in Lasswade Road at 10:30 on Thursday.
The man is due to appear at Edinburgh Sheriff Court on Monday.
